Package it.uniroma2.sel.simlab.jeqn.waiting.policies.dispatchings Description

Provides some example policies for the role dispatching.

The policies in this group are defined according to the Policy structure of it.uniroma2.info.sel.simlab.jeqn.policies

A policy belonging to this group must follow the below GenericType definition:

  • Implicit Input : undefined
  • State : undefined
  • Decision Data : UserBasedDecisionData
  • Decision : UserQueue
